description: Ultra-detailed 8K manga panel. A busy Canadian street food market, colorful stalls, kids and families.
characters: Hotdog: expressive, golden bun, white gloves, chef hat, animated smile. Drone: sleek, red spotlight, digital scanner.

description: Hotdog stands proudly at a cart labeled 'Comfort Food Since 1926', handing food to happy kids.
characters: Hotdog: expressive, proud pose, white gloves, chef hat, animated smile. Surrounded by diverse, smiling families.

description: Inset panel: Police drone scans hotdog from above. Red hologram flashes: 'CATEGORY UNCLEAR'.
characters: Drone: hovering above, glowing red lens. Hotdog: expressive, golden bun, white gloves, chef hat, animated confused looks up slightly, still smiling, unaware.
